posting_body: ['Tanager Creek Townhomes', '2 Bedroom Townhome, 1382 sqft', 'We are Practicing social distancing.', 'We have several alternatives to showing you your new home.', 'Contact us, we would love to discuss the details with you', '3D Tour:Hawthorne 2-Bedroom / 1.5-Bath:  <URL> Now to July 15th Renting from $1999', 'We pay for: Trash, Water, Sewage and all Landscaping!', 'Residents are only responsible for Gas and Electric!', '$1999 per month, 2 bedrooms, 1 full bath upstairs, 1 half baths on main level, 1,382 square feet.', 'Our two bedroom homes have TWO HUGE walk in closets for extra storage space and each unit has a linen closet.', ' Each unit has its own washer and dryer and', 'large walk in pantry off the kitchen', 'Proudly in Eden Prairie school district', 'With Nine Mile Creek running adjacent to the property and protected conservation areas surrounding Tanagers property lines you will enjoy listening to birds (even Loons!), seeing wildlife and a community feel that is unlike any other.', 'Tanager’s location cant be beat.', 'Eden', 'Prairie offers 1,000 acres of developed park land and 200 miles or multi-use trails.', 'Our townhomes have the convenience of your own:', 'Your own front door', '(no shared entry areas or hallways)', 'Your own washer & dryer', '(no community laundry rooms)', 'Central Air conditioning', 'Central heat', 'Cable-ready', '1 Car Garage', 'Dishwasher', 'Microwave', 'Allows Cats', 'Allows Dogs', 'Please give us a call to hear all that Tanager Creek Townhomes has to offer.', 'Key Words: Eden Prairie, Minnetonka, Plymouth, Maple Grove, Hopkins, Wayzata, Waconia, Minnetrista, Eden Prairie School District, Lake Minnetonka, Golden Valley, Bloomington, Chaska, Chanhassen, Victoria, Mound, Waconia, 2 Bedroom Apartment, 3 Bedroom Apartment, Townhouse, Townhome, Town House, Town Home,', 'Pet Friendly, Dogs & Cats Accepted', '<URL>']
